X11-Xlib
========

This module provides low-level and high-level access to X11 libary functions.

This includes access to some X11 extensions like the X11 test library (Xtst).

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other libraries:

    X11
    Xtest
    Xext

and has support for these optional libraries:

    Xcomposite
    Xfixes
    Xrender

